{"tid":590532,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"BENZ, BMW, Audi, Jaguar 品牌定位,你點比較？","createTime":"2018-03-12T16:50:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T07:37:37.000Z","uid":170420,"like":4,"dislike":100,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"369dc5d2b5332223b5dbff09bcf2a499c21f200e","tid":590532,"uid":170420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T16:50:33.000Z","msg":"我講先(只是個人感覺)，用最直觀既感受: <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBENZ: <br />\n(似35-45歲，剛剛事業有成就的精練男人）<br />\n<br />\n身型苗條，斯文有禮，精練，中產，白色，整潔。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBMW: <br />\n（似45歲，剛剛事業已經有所成就的男人，他經歷也很多艱苦的時候，沒有太多文化水平，但頗有錢）<br />\n<br />\n粗豪，笨重，灰色，銀色，財不算大但氣粗，虛榮。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAudi:<br />\n（似25-30歲，剛剛到社會工作的年輕人，每天關注吃喝玩樂。）<br />\n<br />\n年輕，活力，時尚，變化。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJaguar:<br />\n似45-55歲，已經事業有成，準備退休的企業老闆。<br />\n<br />\n成熟，穩重，紳士，淡然，老練，舒泰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申： <br />\n上面只是個人直觀感覺，由於大家接觸人群不同，感受都會吾一樣。<br />\n我呢種比較或許無乜說服力，歡迎大家討論。"},{"pid":"c735ae7879554d07787d8e77629420a0891422b5","tid":590532,"uid":38411,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T16:51:20.000Z","msg":"吾你老母"},{"pid":"d9f0116961012afd78cff837053f71663355ae1b","tid":590532,"uid":41642,"like":61,"dislike":0,"score":61,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T17:09:12.000Z","msg":"得罪講句 完全唔知呢個post有咩討論價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b5016ed34bf777ab4e104e27fef021fe992e157","tid":590532,"uid":22585,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T17:19:22.000Z","msg":"樓主不如行轉港島區，成街P 牌 BBA <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48a3f9fd2d411a001e2c83258aa51819a2780590","tid":590532,"uid":4934,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T01:17:11.000Z","msg":"定位係睇車款唔係睇牌子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfad9c42183460fab5070bd86af9997701bb8090","tid":590532,"uid":174766,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"48a3f9f